1. Molim te, donesi mi flašu vode. (*flašu*) (Please bring me a bottle of water.)
2. Izlio je čašu vode iz flaše. (*flaše*) (He poured a glass of water from the bottle.)
3. Da li si siguran da si dobro zatvorio flašu? (*flašu*) (Are you sure you closed the bottle tightly?)
4. Stavi flašu na sto. (*flašu*) (Put the bottle on the table.)
5. Ova flaša je teška. (*flaša*) (This bottle is heavy.)
6. Moja sestra voli da sakuplja stare flaše. (*flaše*) (My sister likes to collect old bottles.)
7. Prodao sam staru flašu za sto dinara. (*flašu*) (I sold an old bottle for a hundred dinars.)
8. Čuo sam zvuk razbijanja flaše. (*flaše*) (I heard the sound of a bottle breaking.)
9. Pijem vodu iz plastične flaše. (*flaše*) (I'm drinking water from a plastic bottle.)
10. Našao sam staru flašu vina u podrumu. (*flašu*) (I found an old bottle of wine in the cellar.)